headline: What PayPal Holdings (PYPL)'s Push Into AI-Powered Commerce Means for Shareholders
summary: In recent days, Wix.com Ltd. announced a strategic collaboration with PayPal Inc. to bring AI-powered product discovery and commerce to Wix merchants, while PayPal also revealed partnerships enabling entry into major AI channels and integrations with leading e-commerce platforms like BigCommerce and Feedonomics.
